OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1780959783
OL,3,CHuge earthquake hits Philippines
OL,4,Ckilling 12 people and triggering
OL,5,Ctsunami
OL,7,FAn offshore magnitude 7.8 earthquake
OL,8,Fhas rocked southern Philippines,
OL,9,Fkilling at least 12 people and
OL,10,Finjuring hundreds of others.
OL,12,FThe quake struck Monday just after
OL,13,F7.30am, causing significant damage to
OL,14,Fbuildings in the Mindanao region and
OL,15,Ftriggering a three-foot tsunami on the
OL,16,Fnearby coasts, officials said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
