OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1780959783
OL,3,CHuge earthquake hits Philippines
OL,4,Ckilling 12 people and triggering
OL,5,Ctsunami
OL,7,F"It's a major earthquake and we're
OL,8,Fexpecting damage and we've already
OL,9,Fseen some damaged buildings based on
OL,10,Fvideos we've seen," Teresito Bacolcol,
OL,11,Fthe director of the Philippine
OL,12,FInstitute of Volcanology and
OL,13,FSeismology, said.
OL,15,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
