OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1780959783
OL,3,CHuge earthquake hits Philippines
OL,4,Ckilling 12 people and triggering
OL,5,Ctsunami
OL,7,FAt least seven people were killed and
OL,8,Fabout 130 others injured in General
OL,9,FSantos, according to Rod Sosmena, the
OL,10,Fregional director of the Office of
OL,11,FCivil Defence.
OL,13,FA few small buildings partially
OL,14,Fcollapsed and several structures,
OL,15,Fincluding a key access bridge,
OL,16,Fsustained dangerous cracks, Sosmena
OL,17,Fsaid.
OL,26,@qD@_TwxD@bTw
