PN,30904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1780959783
OL,3,CHuge earthquake hits Philippines
OL,4,Ckilling 12 people and triggering
OL,5,Ctsunami
OL,7,FFive other people were killed in the
OL,8,Fsouthern provinces of South Cotabato
OL,9,Fand Davao Occidental province, and on
OL,10,FBalut Island.
OL,12,FSosmena said authorities were checking
OL,13,Freports of some students being trapped
OL,14,Fin a two-storey school that collapsed
OL,15,Fin General Santos, while the national
OL,16,Fpolice said at least seven people were
OL,17,Fmissing in the area.
OL,26,@tD@FTw
