PN,30905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1780959783
OL,3,CHuge earthquake hits Philippines
OL,4,Ckilling 12 people and triggering
OL,5,Ctsunami
OL,7,FPublic schools had reopened nationwide
OL,8,Fon Monday after the summer break, and
OL,9,Fmore than 100 students attending
OL,10,Fmorning flag-raising ceremonies
OL,11,Fsustained bruises during the quake,
OL,12,Fofficial Ednar Dayanghirang said.
OL,14,FFootage shared on social media showed
OL,15,Fthe children gathered with their
OL,16,Fteachers outside before parts of their
OL,17,Fschool building collapsed behind them.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
