PN,30906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1780959783
OL,3,CHuge earthquake hits Philippines
OL,4,Ckilling 12 people and triggering
OL,5,Ctsunami
OL,7,FDayanghirang said he was able to
OL,8,F"hardly stand and keep my balance"
OL,9,Fwhen leaving his house in the southern
OL,10,Fport city of Davao.
OL,12,FNumerous aftershocks followed the
OL,13,Fquake, which was also felt in
OL,14,FMalaysia, with tsunami warnings issued
OL,15,Facross Japan, Indonesia and Malaysia.
OL,17,FThe US Geological Survey reported the
OL,18,Fdepth of the original quake at 55
OL,19,Fkilometres (34 miles), but variations
OL,20,Fin measurements may differ by agency.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
