OL,3,CHuge earthquake hits Philippines
OL,4,Ckilling 12 people and triggering
OL,5,Ctsunami
OL,7,FThe Philippines, one of the world's
OL,8,Fmost disaster-prone countries, is
OL,9,Foften hit by earthquakes and volcanic
OL,10,Feruptions due to its location on the
OL,11,FPacific "Ring of Fire," an arc of
OL,12,Fseismic faults around the ocean.
OL,14,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,15,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,16,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,17,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,18,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,19,Fbelow...
